<h1>Try the carnival guessing game!</h1>
<p>Pick a whole number between 0 and 1000. Enter a number of dollars below to bet that I cannot find your number in 10 guesses or less.</p>
<p>Each time I make a guess, tell me whether I am correct, too high or too low. If I haven't got your number after 10 guesses I will pay you ten times the amount of your bet. Otherwise I keep your money.</p>
